<h1>Money</h1>

<p class="h">
<b>The measure of value, medium of exchange, a store of value</b>
</p>

<p class="h">
<a href="img/logo/600x600.jpg"><img src="img/logo/300x300.jpg"/></a>
</p>


<p class="h2">
<a href="libre/en">LibreMoney</a>
</p>


<p>
<b>Money</b> is a MEASURE, which is the universal equivalent of value of goods and services.
<br/>
Functions of money:
<br/>
- The measure of value;
<br/>
- The medium of exchange;
<br/>
- <i>Storage means (controversial statement)</i>.
</p>

